CREATE TABLE all_group(
            id      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
            numberGroup   TEXT NOT NULL
        )

CREATE TABLE time_lesson(
            id      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
            timeLesson   TEXT NOT NULL
        )

CREATE TABLE address(
            id      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
            keyWord TEXT NOT NULL,
            nameAddress   TEXT NOT NULL,
            linkAddress TEXT NOT NULL
        )

CREATE TABLE all_users(
            id      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
            idUsers   INTEGER NOT NULL,
            nameUsers TEXT,
            lastNameUsers TEXT,
            logitUsers TEXT,
            textGroup TEXT NOT NULL
        )

CREATE TABLE day_of_week(
            id      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
            dayWeek   TEXT NOT NULL
        )

CREATE TABLE information(
            id      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
            buttonnName   TEXT NOT NULL,
            numberPhone TEXT NOT NULL,
            addPhoneNumber TEXT,
            email TEXT NOT NULL
        )

CREATE TABLE "access"
(
	id_users int not null,
	admin_value int,
	manager_value int,
	tester_value int,
	database_tester int
)
